    "project_desc": "Ptolemaeus Arabus et Latinus (PAL) is a long-term project dedicated to the edition and study of the Arabic and Latin versions of Ptolemy’s astronomical and astrological texts and related material. The texts are made available in an online database containing catalogues of Arabic and Latin works, images of manuscripts, searchable transcriptions, critically edited texts and a Greek-Arabic-Latin-English glossary of astronomical and astrological terms.",
